    "causal_summary": "Two production advisor scripts resolve filesystem paths one directory too high. `skill_graph_compiler.py` names its root `SKILLS_DIR` but currently lands at `.opencode/`, causing graph compilation to scan non-skill trees. `skill_advisor.py` currently resolves the SQLite database under the skill root instead of `mcp_server/database/`, so the Python parity shim can probe the wrong database path.",
